abstract: >-
  A bilingual (Arabic/English) evidence-based scientific library documenting
  and evaluating methods for reducing the cost of AI inference, training, and
  deployment. The library classifies 60+ techniques across 7 categories by
  evidence strength (practical, emerging, theoretical, rejected) and provides
  a multi-criteria scoring system, evidence ledger, claims registry, and a
  no-hype policy to help developers, companies, and researchers make informed
  cost-reduction decisions.
